ng="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1099347" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-11-20.11.56.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="539" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-11-20.11.40.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099348" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-11-20.11.40-520x580.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-11-20.11.40-520x580.jpg 520w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/螢幕截圖-2022-05-11-20.11.40.jpg 560w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 520px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：影片截圖</p><p>Pillonel 預計完整影片將於數周後面世，並指全靠訂造的包括充電硬件的柔性 PCB，才令他能把改裝部件塞進 AirPods 充電盒的外殼內。他認為改裝後的 AirPods 令日常更便利，使 Pillonel 只攜帶 MacBook Pro 的 USB-C 充電線便可為 iPhone、AirPods 及 MacBook Pro 充電。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-11-12.32.49.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099320" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-11-12.32.49-376x580.png" alt="" width="376" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-11-12.32.49-376x580.png 376w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-11-12.32.49-583x900.png 583w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-11-12.32.49-768x1186.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-11-12.32.49-995x1536.png 995w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-11-12.32.49.png 1004w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 376px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：影片截圖</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_88866"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0BspRDh2Ejk?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源： <a href="https://www.theverge.com/2022/5/10/23064915/usb-c-airpods-mod-lightning-port-ken-pillonel">The Verge</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
